messages.text: Hey there!
Hi! How are you?
I'm doing great, thanks for asking. How about you?
I'm good too. Just working on some projects.
That's awesome. What projects are you working on?
A few different things, mostly web development.
Nice! I love web development. Do you have a favorite framework?
I'm really into React at the moment. You?
React is great! I'm also a fan of Vue.js.
Vue.js is pretty cool too. Have you tried Angular?
Yes, but I found it a bit more complex. Still, it's very powerful.
Agreed. I guess it depends on the project requirements.
Absolutely. What's your favorite part about web development?
I love the creativity and problem-solving aspects. What about you?
Same here. It's rewarding to build something functional and visually appealing.
Totally. Do you work on personal projects or professionally?
A bit of both. How about you?
Mostly personal projects, but I'm looking to go professional.
That's fantastic! Any specific goals in mind?
Just to keep learning and improving. Maybe start freelancing soon.
